msgstr "Q4"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "Kontaktirajte nas"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "Read more about Documents to leverage its full potential!"
msgstr "Preberite več o Dokumentih, da izkoristite njihov polni potencial!"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model:documents.document,name:accounting_firm.document_request_third_company
msgid "Receipt"
msgstr "Prejemnice"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Rename the project at your will to better identify them by customer name or "
"else."
msgstr ""
"Projekt lahko po želji preimenujete, da ga boste bolje prepoznali po imenu "
"stranke ali kaj drugega."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "Saving the task will report this time in the sale order for billing."
msgstr ""
"Shranjevanje opravila bo ta čas zabeležen v prodajnem naročilu za "
"obračunavanje."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Select the corresponding products or leverage a quotation template, the "
"\"Monthly VAT - Package\" typically."
msgstr ""
"Izberite ustrezne izdelke ali uporabite predlogo za ponudbo, običajno "
"»Mesečni DDV – paket«."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Send this quote by email so that you new customer confirm the mission and "
"accept your fees."
msgstr ""
"Pošljite to ponudbo po e-pošti, da vaša nova stranka potrdi misijo in "
"sprejme vaše stroške."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model:planning.role,name:accounting_firm.planning_role_1
msgid "Senior Accountant"
msgstr "Višji računovodja"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model:project.tags,name:accounting_firm.project_tags_17
msgid "September"
msgstr "September"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Set the recurrence for tasks not coming from the project template and the "
"dead line dates to all project tasks."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite ponavljanje za opravila, ki ne izvirajo iz predloge projekta, in "
"roke za vsa projektna opravila."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Since a tedious part of the job is to request and organise documents for "
"reference and traceability, a good document management system is required!"
msgstr ""
"Ker je zahtevo in organiziranje dokumentov za referenco in sledljivost "
"dolgočasen del dela, je potreben dober sistem za upravljanje dokumentov!"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Some of your services might be time sheet invoiced. You can proceed by "
"different ways to record your time."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere vaše storitve se lahko zaračunavajo po delovnem listu. Čas lahko "
"beležite na različne načine."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:accounting_firm.project_project_1
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:accounting_firm.project_project_3
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:accounting_firm.project_project_6
msgid "Tasks"
msgstr "Opravila"

