msgstr "Predloga / Računovodstvo - Četrtletni DDV"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Accounting Firm package does not include any customization. Note that "
"<strong>Studio App </strong>would enable you to setup specific fields for "
"more robustness as well as much more advanced workflows and automations!"
msgstr ""
"Paket računovodskega podjetja ne vključuje nobenih prilagoditev. "
"Upoštevajte, da vam <strong>Aplikacija Studio </strong>omogoča nastavitev "
"določenih polj za večjo robustnost ter veliko naprednejše delovne procese in"
" avtomatizacijo!"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Accounting Firm package is of great help but may not cover all your needs...<br/>\n"
"            Fortunately, Odoo got you covered:"
msgstr ""
"Paket računovodskega podjetja je v veliko pomoč, vendar morda ne bo pokril vseh vaših potreb ...<br/>\n"
"            Na srečo je Odoo poskrbel za vas:"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Customer onboarding task contains details about actions to take to have "
"your customer in order."
msgstr ""
"Naloga uvajanja strank vsebuje podrobnosti o ukrepih, ki jih je treba "
"izvesti, da bo vaša stranka v redu."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The documents sent to the email alias of this project will arrive in the "
"root folder of the project. This can be considered as an inbox while sub "
"folders contain treated documents in an organized fashion."
msgstr ""
"Dokumenti, poslani na e-poštni vzdevek tega projekta, bodo prispeli v "
"korensko mapo projekta. To lahko štejemo za mapo »Prejeto«, medtem ko "
"podmape vsebujejo obdelane dokumente na organiziran način."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "The project creation created as well some tasks to handle from now on."
msgstr ""
"Z ustvarjanjem projekta so nastale tudi nekatere naloge, ki jih je treba "
"obravnavati od zdaj naprej."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This creates an empty document in your project to be filled by your customer"
" by uploading a file from the email they receive. You could do so for all "
"required documents by the task."
msgstr ""
"S tem se v vašem projektu ustvari prazen dokument, ki ga stranka izpolni z "
"nalaganjem datoteke iz prejetega e-poštnega sporočila. To lahko storite za "
"vse zahtevane dokumente za nalogo."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "Time management"
msgstr "Upravljanje časa"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To assign the Project Manager, open the Project App and open the settings of"
" the project, clicking the three dots in the top right corner of the "
"corresponding tile."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodeliti vodjo projekta, odprite aplikacijo Project in nato "
"nastavitve projekta tako, da kliknete tri pike v zgornjem desnem kotu "
"ustrezne ploščice."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To request a document such as an ID card or a bank statement, click New and "
"then Request."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zahtevati dokument, kot je osebna izkaznica ali bančni izpisek, "
"kliknite Novo in nato Zahtevaj."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To setup the project folder email alias, display the project top bar and add"
" the Documents shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti vzdevek e-pošte za mapo projekta, prikažite zgornjo "
"vrstico projekta in dodajte bližnjico Dokumenti."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model:mail.activity.type,name:accounting_firm.mail_activity_ubo_update
#: model:mail.activity.type,summary:accounting_firm.mail_activity_ubo_update
msgid "UBO update"
msgstr "Posodobitev UBO"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model:project.tags,name:accounting_firm.project_tags_3
msgid "Ultimate Beneficial Owners"
msgstr "Končni dejanski lastniki"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model:product.template,name:accounting_firm.product_product_6_product_template
msgid "Ultimate Beneficial Owners register (Pack)"
msgstr "Register končnih dejanskih lastnikov (paket)"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Odoo Accounting Firm package! This guide will help you manage"
" your missions efficiently from opportunity management to billing, as well "
"as requesting documents."
msgstr ""
"Dobrodošli v paketu računovodskega podjetja Odoo! Ta vodnik vam bo pomagal "
"učinkovito upravljati vaše naloge, od upravljanja priložnosti do "
"obračunavanja in zahtevanja dokumentov."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "Welcoming prospects"
msgstr "Dobrodošli potencialni kupci"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When you confirm a sale order, know that the duplicated project is defined in the product you sold. You can edit the project to adjust the list for customer onboarding actions or folder architecture so that you save\n"
"                    time in the future."
msgstr ""
"Ko potrdite prodajno naročilo, vedite, da je podvojeni projekt definiran v izdelku, ki ste ga prodali. Projekt lahko uredite, da prilagodite seznam za dejanja uvajanja strank ali arhitekturo map, da prihranite\n"
"                    čas v prihodnosti."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Whether you performed some work for a fixed price or based on time sheets, "
"you can expense your customer for this."
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na to, ali ste delo opravili za fiksno ceno ali na podlagi "
"delovnega časa, lahko to stranki zaračunate kot stroške."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or explore more features?"
msgstr ""
"Bi se radi z nami pogovorili o svoji nastavitvi Odoo ali raziskali več "
"funkcij?"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Yet be aware that by default, any email sent to info@yourcompanyname.example.com will create a new lead in your CRM pipeline!<br/>\n"
"                    You can verify this by opening the CRM App, opening the sales teams from the Configuration menu, and opening the sales team you have."
msgstr ""
"Vendar ne pozabite, da bo vsako e-poštno sporočilo, poslano na info@imevasegapodjetja.primer.com, privzeto ustvarilo novo potencialno stranko v vašem CRM prodajnem procesu!<br/>\n"
"                    To lahko preverite tako, da odprete aplikacijo CRM, v meniju Konfiguracija odprete prodajne ekipe in nato odprete svojo prodajno ekipo."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can as well change view for the list view for example, and click the New"
" button to report some time."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako lahko spremenite pogled na seznam in kliknete gumb Novo, da "
"prijavite nekaj časa."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can as well submit a letter of mission to be digitally signed with the "
"<strong>Sign app</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako lahko s pomočjo<strong>aplikacije Podpis</strong>oddate digitalno "
"podpisano pooblastilo.."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can preview the quote at this stage. This view is for your customer to "
"confirm the mission."
msgstr ""
"Na tej stopnji si lahko predogledate ponudbo. Ta pogled je namenjen temu, da"
" vaša stranka potrdi misijo."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "You can still do it by upgrading your package in Apps."
msgstr ""
"To lahko še vedno storite tako, da nadgradite svoj paket v Aplikacijah."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You have access in the project Dashboard to all related documents and can follow up on earnings and costs effortlessly.<br/>\n"
"                    Don't forget to update your employee costs, in the setting tab, to compute relevant costs."
msgstr ""
"V nadzorni plošči projekta imate dostop do vseh povezanih dokumentov in lahko brez težav spremljate zaslužek in stroške.<br/>\n"
"                    Ne pozabite posodobiti stroškov zaposlenih v zavihku z nastavitvami, da izračunate ustrezne stroške."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just got a all and a customer wants to know more about your rates and "
"services. Rather than sending him an email on the side, leverage the "
"centralised chatter capability and most of all, do not lose this lead!"
msgstr ""
"Pravkar ste prejeli povpraševanje in stranka želi izvedeti več o vaših cenah "
"in storitvah. Namesto da ji pošljete e-pošto, izkoristite centralizirano "
"možnost klepeta in predvsem ne izgubite te potencialne stranke!"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just got a all and a customer wants you for the job, congratulations!"
msgstr "Pravkar si dobil vse in stranka te želi za to delo, čestitam!"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You might have tested the Accounting Firm package with or without demo data.<br/>\n"
"            In any case, you may have written records in journals which are not deletable and which might be an issue for your traceability."
msgstr ""
"Morda ste že preizkusili paket računovodskega podjetja z demo podatki ali brez njih.<br/>\n"
"            V vsakem primeru imate morda pisne zapise v dnevnikih, ki jih ni mogoče izbrisati in ki bi lahko ovirali vašo sledljivost."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You might want to setup questionnaires to fine tune your quotations and "
"clarify the interactions with your customers. Have a look at the "
"<strong>Survey App</strong> to do so!"
msgstr ""
"Morda boste želeli nastaviti vprašalnike, da bi izboljšali svoje ponudbe in "
"razjasnili interakcije s strankami. Oglejte si <strong>Aplikacijo za "
"Ankete</strong>, da to storite!"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your Odoo Accounting Firm package includes essential apps to streamline your"
" operations:"
msgstr ""
"Vaš paket računovodskega podjetja Odoo vključuje bistvene aplikacije za "
"poenostavitev vašega poslovanja:"

